			"content": {
				"number": "2",
				"text": "<span class=\"updated\" title=\"Texten &#xE4;r uppdaterad\">Se även International pressure ulcer guidelines. Publicerade i september 2014. </span><a href=\"http://international-pressure-ulcer-guidelines.myshopify.com/\" target=\"_blank\" class=\"linkOut\">http://international-pressure-ulcer-guidelines.myshopify.com/</a> "
